         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">13/2/82. ¶  ¶ I am much interested in all that you say in your kind letter of the 3 Febr., ¶  dear Mr Buchanan, ¶  and am beholden to you for the sending of various fruits. Alectryon, long ago reduced...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">82.02.13c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To John Buchanan</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">A644, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">13/2/82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am much interested in all that you say in your kind letter of the 3 Febr.,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found.</p>
               </note> dear Mr Buchanan,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="">John Buchanan (1819-1898).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> and am beholden to you for the sending of various fruits. <name key="Alectryon">Alectryon</name>, long ago reduced by me to <name key="Nephelium">Nephelium</name>, has precisely the same beautiful black polished seeds enclosed in a crimson or scarlet aril as several other species of <name key="Nephelium">Nephelium</name>, from which it only differs by the maturation of only one cell of the fruit. What has become of young Mr Travers?<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>H. H. Travers.</p>
               </note> I have lost quite sight of him. Have you characteristic specimens of the Helophyllums &amp; Calthas to spare? If so, would you with your usual generosity let me have a set? I will soon look to the Raoulias, kindly sent by you, but had to finish off arrear work in the Department, which left me no time lately for new work. I am much interested in this <name key="Raoulia%20">Raoulia </name>question and told Hooker so.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>See M to J. Hooker, 20 October 1881.</p>
               </note> The cyperaceous plant, to which you allude, I have not received.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">In Orchids I am particularly interested; would you kindly spare me a specimen of your <name key="Epiblema%20grandiflorum">Epiblema grandiflorum</name> for comparison; its reoccurrence in N.Z. is interesting.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Alectryon">Alectryon</name>
            </p>
